{"tid":649654,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇得block咗人但係依然見到佢開嘅post？","createTime":"2018-05-01T17:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T02:33:51.000Z","uid":51129,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9dd87571b607a4704833f4c86efb140129a507","tid":649654,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n依家嘅普通block，block左之後，係直頭唔知條友開左貼<br />\n<br />\n示範：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/011948_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F011948_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=dd42cc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nblock前，見到會員咩咩妹跳舞有個post響到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/012022_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F012022_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e4ef3b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Show Blocked User - 咩咩妹跳舞)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/012119_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F012119_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=566d34a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nblock左之後，直接冇左佢個post，連show blocked user字眼都冇。<br />\n咁樣唔係我想要嘅效果，依家又唔係玩緊完全封鎖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇得整個「弱版」嘅block功能，淨係block回覆，但係依然可以正常顯示佢開嘅post / 佢開嘅post會顯示(Show blocked user - xxxx)？"},{"pid":"cac0daec6720c37fc610a627489e96500fb517d2","tid":649654,"uid":29606,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:48:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53f5bc385ab6493da2c26fabe3cb4cbcb95083dd","tid":649654,"uid":5190,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cac0daec6720c37fc610a627489e96500fb517d2","tid":649654,"uid":29606,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":